ing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8CzZAZO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8CzZAZO.jpg&h=ffa3883d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XLbtujS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLbtujS.jpg&h=eecd2b06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到隔離都有份報紙嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\">頭版有一格係我哋</span><br />\n不過因為買得太多報紙所以就冇再買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會登到報都係多得大家嘅努力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />命</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b6ca0762267936c2f06948cad0102d022f985b3","tid":1487264,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9b9ef934f8f2bb4a8dc685dfa3cd6c6c2742cea1","tid":1487264,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceac2f154ad2c51d0a3291bcef8ee871ad7f0a55","tid":1487264,"uid":288559,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:55:32.000Z","msg":"補返近照<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4VKOumt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4VKOumt.jpg&h=dfbcde49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15fc878d51d7c587307b7adda11af78c82f5c7e0","tid":1487264,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:56:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a7e211d191c146d449831e4eccd3071a917fd480","tid":1487264,"uid":288559,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"係呢張先啱<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQG1PmP.jpg\" data-thum